title: bunnymunro
description:
The Death of Bunny Munro by Nick Cave.

Bunny Munro sells beauty products and the dream of hope to lonely housewives.
Set adrift by his wife's death and trying to get a grip on reality,he hits the road.
While he plies his trade and his sexual charisma door-to-door, bunny junior sits patiently in the car.
As their bizarre road trip shears in a final reckoning, Bunny finds that the ghosts of his past have emerged from the shadows and are seeking revenge.
